overview: Foxy Croquette Ogin disappeared after the protest incident in front of the National Diet building in 1960, but there are rumors of a mysterious Japanese woman amongst a band of guerillas in Palestine...
title: Female Fast Food Grifter: Foxy Croquette Ogin ~Mortal Struggle in Palestine~
